|----------|-------------|-------------|-----------|
| Database | `sqlx::Error`, `tokio_postgres::Error` | 500 | High |
| Cache | `redis::RedisError` | 500 | High |
| Validation | `validator::ValidationErrors`, `String` | 400 | High |
| Not Found | Custom variants | 404 | Medium |
| Authentication | Custom variants | 401 | Low |
| Authorization | Custom variants | 403 | Low |
